                            </svg>
                            <h6 class="mt-4">EMERGENCY</h6>
                            <p>(+353) 333 333 333</p>
                            <p>(+1) 333 333 333</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <div class="box-contact">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="34" height="34" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-geo-alt" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                <path d="M12.166 8.94c-.524 1.062-1.234 2.12-1.96 3.07A31.493 31.493 0 0 1 8 14.58a31.481 31.481 0 0 1-2.206-2.57c-.726-.95-1.436-2.008-1.96-3.07C3.304 7.867 3 6.862 3 6a5 5 0 0 1 10 0c0 .862-.305 1.867-.834 2.94zM8 16s6-5.686 6-10A6 6 0 0 0 2 6c0 4.314 6 10 6 10z" />
                                <path d="M8 8a2 2 0 1 1 0-4 2 2 0 0 1 0 4zm0 1a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6z" />
                            </svg>
                            <h6 class="mt-4">LOCATION</h6>
                            <p>000 Someone Place</p>
                            <p>000 Someone Country</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <div class="box-contact">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="34" height="34" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-envelope" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                <path d="M0 4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4Zm2-1a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v.217l7 4.2 7-4.2V4a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H2Zm13 2.383-4.708 2.825L15 11.105V5.383Zm-.034 6.876-5.64-3.471L8 9.583l-1.326-.795-5.64 3.47A1 1 0 0 0 2 13h12a1 1 0 0 0 .966-.741ZM1 11.105l4.708-2.897L1 5.383v5.722Z" />
                            </svg>
                            <h6 class="mt-4">EMAIL</h6>
                            <p>info@example.com</p>
                            <p>admin@example.com</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <div class="box-contact">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="34" height="34" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-clock" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                <path d="M8 3.5a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0V9a.5.5 0 0 0 .252.434l3.5 2a.5.5 0 0 0 .496-.868L8 8.71V3.5z" />
                                <path d="M8 16A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16zm7-8A7 7 0 1 1 1 8a7 7 0 0 1 14 0z" />
                            </svg>
                            <h6 class="mt-4">WORKING HOURS</h6>
                            <p>Mon-Sat 9:00-20:00</p>
                            <p>Sunday Emergency Only</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-5 mx-auto">
                <form asp-controller="Contact" asp-action="Index">
                    <div class="form-group mb-4">
                        <label for="fullName">Full Name</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name" class="form-control" id="fullName" aria-describedby="fullName" placeholder="your Name">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group mb-4">
                        <label for="email">Email</label>
                        <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="your email">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group mb-4">
                        <label for="exampleFormControlTextarea1">Message</label>
                        <textarea class="form-control" name="message" id="exampleFormControlTextarea1" rows="3" placeholder="your message..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-dark">Submit</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>